title: Jira: Workflow
agents: jira
catalog: app/jira
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 With this check you can monitor the number of Issues for given projects and
 there workflows. It outputs the number of issues of the given project and
 workflow.

 Needs the datasource "Check statistics of Jira" to be configured.

item:
 The item is the name of the project and workflow.

discovery:
 One service is created  for each project and workflow
 {"Jira Workflow My_project/My_workflow"}.
